    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Person is from the Jewish National Front, the lady next to Harry Best.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The chairman of the evening is a friend of mine, Sugarman, Ralph Sugarman, which he went to school with me together in Poland.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the last one at right is the president of the ladies group in the association, Rose Bernstein.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This picture was taken.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's a documentary picture.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the document on top, it's myself, Isadore Hollander, taken in Germany 50 years ago.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I am standing in front, holding the picture up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were celebrating the liberation and the cooperation from the HIAS, which they helped to take down the people, DP people from Germany.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We're standing in front of the Statue of Liberty in New Jersey, in the United States.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I'm holding up the document, which was given to me in Germany as a member of the HIAS going to the United States.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This picture was taken in Harrisburg, Pennsylvania, as we commemorate every year the anniversary of the Shoah.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We are invited to the mention into the capital of the states.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And here, we are celebrating the anniversary, which, from left, is my daughter, Miriam, one of my grandsons, Stephen, myself, Isadore, my little granddaughter.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Behind is my wife, Anni, my daughter next to her, Shirley, and two little grandchildrens, Dina and Justin.",
